data.description: Welcome to 523 Sweetleaf Dr in the Bloomingdale community of Brandon, FL. three spacious bedrooms and two re-designed bathrooms. 2 car garage, providing convenience and security for your vehicle. perfect for everyday living and entertaining, with new wood like tile throughout the entire home. Fully equipped kitchen that opens to the dining area delivering a seamless blend of functionality and style, 2 large sliders off the living and dining rooms bring in an abundance of light into the home and allows views of the spacious screened in lanai and fully fenced backyard. a delightful home in the heart of Brandon. Brand new roof and HVAC Quaint community conveniently located just minutes away from the Westfield Mall, shops, restaurants, I-75 and I-4.
